<h3>Install</h3>

<pre><code><span class="code"><span class="paren1">(<span class="code">ql:quickload <span class="keyword">:cl-async</span></span>)</span></span></code></pre>

<p>Please be aware that until cl-async v0.6.x is in quicklisp, you might want to
git clone the master branch into <code>quicklisp/local-projects/</code>.</p>

<h3>Tests</h3>

<p>There is a fairly complete suite of tests in the <code>cl-async-test</code> package:</p>

<pre><code><span class="code"><span class="paren1">(<span class="code">ql:quickload <span class="keyword">:cl-async-test</span></span>)</span>
<span class="paren1">(<span class="code">cl-async-test:run-tests</span>)</span>
<span class="paren1">(<span class="code">cl-async-test:run-tests <span class="keyword">:ssl</span> t</span>)</span>
<span class="paren1">(<span class="code">cl-async-test:run-tests <span class="keyword">:threading</span> t</span>)</span></span></code></pre>

